data.description:
This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a 1-car garage boasts a fresh and inviting atmosphere. Step into a well-maintained space featuring walk-in closets in both bedrooms, complemented by carpeting in the bedrooms. The main living areas showcase stylish tile flooring, creating a seamless flow throughout.

The kitchen is a highlight, adorned with elegant wood cabinetry and sleek granite countertops, offering a perfect blend of functionality and aesthetics. The property includes an enclosed porch for relaxing moments and a spacious yard featuring a shed, ideal for outdoor activities and storage needs.

Situated in the desirable Sebring Hills neighborhood, residents can relish the convenience of proximity to shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and boating opportunities. Don't miss the chance to call this sweet and clean home yours, where comfort and style harmonize seamlessly."
